  "prompt": "Which is the best coaching in Patna for the IIT-JEE?",
  "response": "Determining the \"best\" coaching institute for IIT-JEE in Patna depends on various factors such as teaching quality, faculty, infrastructure, results, and individual preferences. However, some of the most reputed and popular coaching institutes in Patna for IIT-JEE preparation are:\n\n1. **Resonance Eduventures Ltd.**  \n   - Known for its structured study material and experienced faculty.  \n   - Offers both classroom and online programs.  \n   - Consistently produces good results in IIT-JEE.  \n\n2. **Allen Career Institute**  \n   - One of the most popular coaching institutes in India.  \n   - Known for its rigorous test series and experienced faculty.  \n   - Provides extensive study material and parent-teacher interactions.  \n\n3. **Aakash Institute**  \n   - Offers comprehensive classroom and online coaching.  \n   - Known for its quality study material and test series.  \n   - Focuses on individual attention and doubt-clearing sessions.  \n\n4. **Motion Institute**  \n   - Provides a combination of coaching and test series for IIT-JEE.  \n   - Known for its experienced faculty and result-oriented approach.  \n\n5. **Career Point**  \n   - Offers classroom and online programs for IIT-JEE aspirants.  \n   - Known for its study material and doubt-solving sessions.  \n\n6. **Super 30** (No formal coaching institute, but highly reputed)  \n   - A program by Anand Kumar that prepares underprivileged students for IIT-JEE.  \n   - Highly selective and known for its success rate.  \n\n7. **Cadd Galaxy**  \n   - Popular among students in Patna.  \n   - Focuses on personalized attention and regular tests.  \n\nWhile these institutes are well-regarded, it's essential to visit their centers, interact with faculty, and evaluate their teaching methodologies to determine which one aligns best with your learning style and needs. Additionally, consider factors like batch size, location, and fees before making a decision.",
